Joe Hasham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Hasham 0 Joseph Christopher Hasham (OAM) (Arabic: جو هشام‎) (born 4 September 1948 Tripoli, Lebanon) is a Lebanese Australian actor who became famous in Australia in the 1970s through his long running role of dependable and decent gay lawyer Don Finlayson in soap opera Number 96.
